{"tid":315882,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"潮文．潮圖討論(集思廣益)","createTime":"2017-07-10T10:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T11:29:30.000Z","uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8fb06ddec7c807eff1559ba603f4820a97d40540","tid":315882,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T10:37:44.000Z","msg":"想知點解D好耐冇出現既潮文或者潮圖，巴/絲打一陣(幾分鐘)就可以quote 出來，其實係咪bookmark 好晒?好想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"119ef8b8568bf099a0f601b90ea4be8e40833105","tid":315882,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T10:39:25.000Z","msg":"先黎一篇會一會各位先：<br />\n<br />\n其實牛排衣家野，同海鮮一樣，靚既唔洗搞甘多調味，鹽同黑白椒就ok，最多加D Rosemary番茜，甚至係超市買支Season $4X~6X一支就搞掂，只有肉質差既先要搞花臣，所以咁樣不如慳D錢去Citysuper或者其他出口店買勁靚牛排返屋企整仲好啦"},{"pid":"74499e70026524307063a8c0e488b4a044c6d66f","tid":315882,"uid":8175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T10:44:06.000Z","msg":"上google search就有啦懵薯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d11a2c3f27463993b134adee9bee9b37175c4af","tid":315882,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T10:45:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上google search就有啦懵薯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n集思廣益嘛，或者有其他方法呢，傻蛋"},{"pid":"c283c4033563422fddf2ace9b6a2ba696bd16d80","tid":315882,"uid":2950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T11:10:19.000Z","msg":"我以前都係咁諗<br />\n但係有一日我鼓起勇氣<br />\n一野拉左個女仔係後樓梯到<br />\n之係你眼望我眼<br />\n當佢想口聲個陣<br />\n我就一野嘴左落去<br />\n佢目定口呆咁望著我<br />\n過左呢件事<br />\n佢就從屌我嘴佢開始去到唔同既話題<br />\n一直跟住我後面<br />\n雖然我好少出聲應佢<br />\n但係佢都一直同我講野<br />\n估唔到我地咁快就打破左互相既隔膜<br />\n直到第三日<br />\n<br />\n我係監獄入面等緊放飯"},{"pid":"c4e9a970e109d60e9fe236d95c08d8746bdc73fe","tid":315882,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T11:27:58.000Z","msg":"Onj"},{"pid":"8c9e4840938228be0b3eb0f312c7b0c3cd9f800b","tid":315882,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T11:29:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}